From b768e36602d690fd234646f4bbe809710dd011bf Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Tue, 16 Jun 2026 16:04:24 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Tutorial highlight system: step-by-step hints + pulse
 animation
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Add tutorialHint/tutorialTarget state for per-phase guidance
- setTutorial() helper + hl() className helper for pulse highlight
- Phase useEffect: updates hint text + target on every phase transition
- dealtCount useEffect: updates P/B target during dealing (4 steps)
- payWB.step useEffect: updates target through pay/comm/collect/refund
- CSS @keyframes thl + .thl class: gold outline pulse animation
- Fixed bottom hint bar: compass icon + message + dismiss (X)
- Wrapped key buttons with hl() divs for pulse outline:
  nomorebets, reject-latebet, deal-P/B, open-btn (×4),
  player-draw, banker-draw, settle-take, confirm-take,
  pay-confirm, collect-confirm, refund-confirm, chat-end
- bettingDone useEffect: enables nomorebets highlight when ready

https://claude.ai/code/session_01DRkieVn1g8u7ZV43TWZBxY
